name: lms-swagger
description: Auto generated Swagger documentation for the Library Management system micro services: borrower-microservice, librarian-microservice, administrator-microservice.

name: utopia-airline-system
description: This project uses a microservice architecture using submodules to create an airline reservation system.

name: lms-librarian-microservice
description: This service is apart of the Librarian Management System. It provides functionality for Librarians to manage a Library branch.

name: lms-administrator-microservice
description: This service is apart of the Librarayy Management System. It provides the functionality for Admins to manage a Library.

name: Microservices_IS4_Identity_Template
description: Microservices based architecture with an IdentityServer4 OpenID OAuth and ASP Net Identity user system

name: lms-borrower-microservice
description: This Microservice is apart of the Library Management System. This service provides a REST API for managing the borrower user functionality

name: utopia-counter-microservice
description: This microservice is apart of the Utopia Airline System. It provides functionality for a counter agent to perform all needed tasks for managing a customers reservation.

name: utopia-user-microservice
description: This microservice is apart of the Utopia Airline System. It provides the functionality for producing and authenticating JSON Web Tokens for the online, agent and counter usertypes.

name: utopia-agent-microservice
description: This is a microservice apart of the Utopia Airline System. It provides the needed functionality for a travel agent to book or cancel a flight for a customer.

name: utopia-online-microservice
description: This microservice is apart of the Utopia Airline System. It provides functionality for a customer to make a flight reservation online without having to interact with another person.

name: Java_backend_cars_website
description: A REST API used as a backend system for a cars website with an in-memory H2 database, using microservices to get specific prices and car's location.
